## Account Resource Monitor Configuration

### Configuration Summary

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Monitor Name** | `account_resource_monitor` |
| **Credit Limit** | {{ account_resource_monitor_limit }} credits |
| **Action at Limit** | {{ account_resource_monitor_action }} |
| **Reset Frequency** | {{ account_resource_monitor_reset_frequency }} |
| **Scope** | Account-wide (all warehouses) |

### How the Monitor Works
{%- if account_resource_monitor_action == "Suspend Immediately" %}

**Suspend Immediately Selected**

When the credit limit is reached, all warehouses will be **immediately suspended**, stopping all running queries.

| Impact | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Running queries | ❌ Cancelled immediately |
| New queries | ❌ Blocked |
| Warehouses | ❌ Suspended |
{%- elif account_resource_monitor_action == "Suspend After Current Queries" %}

**Suspend After Current Queries Selected**

When the credit limit is reached, warehouses will be **suspended after current queries complete**.

| Impact | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Running queries | ✅ Complete normally |
| New queries | ❌ Blocked |
| Warehouses | ❌ Suspended after current work |
{%- else %}

**Notify Only Selected**

When the credit limit is reached, **alerts will be sent** but warehouses will continue running.

| Impact | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| Running queries | ✅ Continue |
| New queries | ✅ Allowed |
| Cost protection | ⚠️ Manual intervention required |
{%- endif %}

### Alert Thresholds (Tiered Protection)

| Credit Level | Percentage | Action | Purpose |
|--------------|------------|--------|---------|
| {{ (account_resource_monitor_limit | int * 0.75) | round | int }} credits | 75% | Notify | Early warning |
| {{ (account_resource_monitor_limit | int * 0.90) | round | int }} credits | 90% | Notify | Final warning |
| {{ account_resource_monitor_limit }} credits | 100% | {{ account_resource_monitor_action }} | Limit enforcement |

### How Budgets + Resource Monitors Work Together

| Tool | Alert Type | When It Fires | Action |
|------|------------|---------------|--------|
| **Budget** | Predictive | When *projected* to exceed threshold | Notify only |
| **Resource Monitor** | Actual | When *actually* reaching threshold | Notify or Suspend |

**Example Timeline:**
1. Day 10: Budget forecasts you'll hit 75% → Alert sent (early warning based on trend)
2. Day 18: Resource monitor hits 75% actual usage → Alert sent (real-time confirmation)
3. Day 24: Resource monitor hits 90% → Alert sent (final warning)
4. Day 28: Resource monitor hits 100% → {{ account_resource_monitor_action }}

### Emergency Procedures

If the resource monitor suspends warehouses unexpectedly:

1. **Assess Situation**: Determine why limit was reached
2. **Increase Limit**: `ALTER RESOURCE MONITOR account_resource_monitor SET CREDIT_QUOTA = <new_limit>;`
3. **Resume Warehouses**: Manually resume suspended warehouses
4. **Investigate**: Identify cause of high usage